@NODE les_introduction
Introduction
============

Who are Leading Edge Software?
------------------------------

Leading Edge Software is a team of university students (and staff) aiming
to produce quality software for the Amiga range of computers.

The LES team:

Steven McNamara - Code,Documentation,Gfx ( 68000 expert :-) )
Steven Matty    - Code,Documentation,Gfx,Sampling
Steven Green    - Code?,Documentation,Gfx,Sampling
Steven Innell   - Music,Documentation,3D Gfx
Robert Brennan  - Gfx
Nigel Hughes    - Code,Documentation,Gfx
Mike Richards   - Gfx

The first project to be undertaken by the group was a user friendly Map
Editor suitable not only for games but many other applications as well
(this will become apparent further within these docs). Enjoy :-)


Contact us!
===========

